<sentence id="4">Identification of autophagy receptors , such as p62/SQSTM1 and NBR1 , which simultaneously bind both ubiquitin and autophagy-specific ubiquitin-like modifiers , LC3/GABARAP , has provided a molecular link between ubiquitination and autophagy .</sentence>
